Since $a^2 \le n$ and $b^2 \le n,$ $a^4 \le n^2 = 64a^4 b^4$ and $b^4 \le n^2 = 64a^4 b^4,$ so $64a^4 b^4 \ge 1.$  Hence, $a^4 b^4 \ge \frac{1}{64},$ so $ab \ge \frac{1}{2}.$

