Since we can make these choices independently for each of the $64$ unit squares, the total number of colorings is $6^{64} \cdot 5^{64} \cdot 4^{64} = 2^{192} \cdot 3^{64} \cdot 5^{64}$.  The answer is $192 + 64 + 64 = \boxed{320}$. 

